LIDDY: Miep!
MIEP: Oh.

17:00.686 --> 17:03.356
Liddy and Alfred,
hello you two.

17:03.356 --> 17:05.024
Hello.

17:05.024 --> 17:07.109
LIDDY: Uncle Max took us
on an adventure today.

17:07.109 --> 17:08.986
